          "code": "giSine ftgen 1, 0, 4096, 10, 1\ninstr 1\n kfreq chnget \"hostFreq\"\n kgain chnget \"hostGain\"\n a1 oscili kgain * 0.20, kfreq * 2.5, giSine\n a2 oscili kgain * 0.10, kfreq * 3.5, giSine\n outs a1 + a2, a1 - a2\nendin",
